title: Tihad Sportif Casablanca
text: Tihad Sportif Casablanca was a <a href="Morocco">Moroccan</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club that was founded in 1936 and disbanded in 2003 following the merger with <a href="FUS%20Rabat">FUS Rabat</a>. The club still survive in other sports sections, notably including <a href="basketball">basketball</a> and <a href="volleyball">volleyball</a>.
